534
00:38:19.220 --> 00:38:23.223
Hier. Marcalva Industrial Storage.

535
00:38:23.390 --> 00:38:25.516
Echt ergens anders.

536
00:38:26.642 --> 00:38:28.726
Goed gewerkt. jongens.

537
00:38:32.438 --> 00:38:34.523
Wat doe je?

538
00:38:34.940 --> 00:38:36.983
Ik moet ervandoor.

539
